      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CATCH THE FEELS (5) is a well performed dog and winner of seven races who was in the minor money last time out at this track (27.74). Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Good form should continue. BOLT OF FUN (1) is a promising dog in the frame at 14 of 27 starts including eight wins and was in the minors again latest (22.53) over 400m at this track. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Super consistent and can feature with the right run. HUDSON (3) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at Cannington in a handy 30.34 beating Garritty. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. ASTON NERO (2) was out of placings last time (22.83) at this track in a Free For All, finishing fifth and beaten 5 lengths. Has already won four times from this draw.",
